docs\devlog\detailed\2026-04-25_2026-04-25.md-57-**User decisions on open questions:** Q1 = remove `detectInPlaceMutations` and `detectInPlacePositionMutations` entirely (breaking); Q2 = static blocks are entity-less terrain only (Option A, doc-only fix); Q3 = `submit`/`serialize` stay available on poisoned world but warn; Q4 = thread `TComponents`/`TState` through callbacks (Option B); Q5 = FIFO is official resource-transfer priority (doc-only fix).
