docs\reviews\full\2026-04-25\2\raw\codex.stdout.log-1373-1. **C1** ƒ?" `ComponentStore` strict-mode fingerprint waste eliminated; new `detectInPlaceMutations` opt-out.
docs\reviews\full\2026-04-25\2\raw\codex.stdout.log-1374-2. **C2 + H8 + H9** ƒ?" `submit()` now always delegates to `submitWithResult()` so sequence assignment / result emission is consistent across instrumentation profiles. `processCommands` emits `tick_aborted_before_handler` execution events for every command queued for a failed tick.
docs\reviews\full\2026-04-25\2\raw\codex.stdout.log:1375:3. **H1 + H2** ƒ?" Fail-fast tick semantics: `world.poisoned` set on any failure; `step()`/`stepWithResult()` refuse until `world.recover()`. `gameLoop.advance()` runs before diff listeners so `world.tick === diff.tick` during the listener phase. `GameLoop.step()` no longer auto-advances.
docs\reviews\full\2026-04-25\2\raw\codex.stdout.log-1376-4. **H4 + M8 + M9** ƒ?" `destroyEntity` marks the entity dying (alive=false, generation bump) BEFORE callbacks, releases the id only after cleanup completes (try/finally), and pushes destruction-time tag/meta cleanup into `TickDiff`. `SpatialGrid.assertBounds` is now public.
docs\reviews\full\2026-04-25\2\raw\codex.stdout.log-1377-5. **H6 + H7 + M5 + M6 + L8 + L9** ƒ?" Snapshot v5 round-trips `maxTicksPerFrame`, `instrumentationProfile`, and per-component `ComponentStoreOptions`. `EntityManager.fromState` and `ResourceStore.fromState` validate input. `VisibilityMap.getState()` flushes. Deserialize rejects non-integer entity-id keys.
docs\reviews\full\2026-04-25\2\raw\codex.stdout.log-1378-6. **H3 + M1 + M2 + M11** ƒ?" `findNearest` now does an expanding-radius scan with a `seen` dedup set and an early-out when `bestDistSq <= (r-1)Aý`. `getEvents`/`getDiff`/`getByTag`/`getTags` return defensive copies. `ComponentStore.set()` clears `removedSet`. Path queue compaction threshold lowered to 256.
