docs\reviews\done\ENGINE_DESIGN_REVIEW.md:38:Docs encourage direct mutation from `getComponent()` (`docs/guides/concepts.md:58`, `docs/guides/concepts.md:66`), and systems examples mutate component objects in place. But dirty tracking only happens when `ComponentStore.set()` or `ComponentStore.remove()` is called (`src/component-store.ts:10`, `src/component-store.ts:27`). `World.buildDiff()` only reads those dirty sets (`src/world.ts:419`).
