docs\reviews\full\2026-04-25\1\REVIEW.md-302-5. **Snapshot fidelity (H6 + H7 + M5 + M6 + L8 + L9).** v5 snapshot adding `componentOptions`, `maxTicksPerFrame`, `instrumentationProfile`; tighten `fromState` validation across the board; flush VisibilityMap on `getState`.
