docs/api-reference.md-1789-```
docs/api-reference.md-1790-
docs/api-reference.md:1791:Returns a deterministic pseudo-random number in `[0, 1)`. Worlds created with the same `seed` produce the same sequence, and snapshot version 3 stores the RNG state so `World.deserialize()` resumes from the exact next value.
